title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
